msgid "We may update these Terms from time to time. Material changes will be communicated to your registered email address at least 14 days before they take effect. Continued use of the Service after changes take effect constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms. If you do not agree to the new Terms, you must stop using the Service and delete your account."
